{"tid":1368740,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 請求中共基於人道理由接收香港警察及其家屬於大灣區","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:36:34.000Z","uid":156891,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3811d21add6b894881477f1a7be94bcb2d8559d0","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"香港警察為維護中共及特區政府尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n不惜以身試法，大量使用非法武力擊潰示威者<br />\n<br />\n甚至同黑社會聯手，搞到同香港市民反哂面<br />\n<br />\n但依家政務司司長居然帶頭迫害警察<br />\n<br />\n連建制陣營都開始支持獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n變相司法迫害警察，再加上香港市民於語言、精神、心理方面全方位迫害<br />\n<br />\n連同警察家屬亦被起底，一同受到迫害<br />\n<br />\n傷害已造成，無法挽回，局勢持續升溫，拯救香港警察刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n因此，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本人建議中央人民政府基於人道及政治迫害為理由，立刻接收香港警察及其家屬，並安置於大灣區永久居留</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為留係香港既，只有政治、司法、同香港市民既迫害<br />\n<br />\n當然，千其唔好俾佢地番黎香港啦"},{"pid":"5d0d9099598dc2ba6a99b7bad88a1626c888c20e","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"我唔係9up架，如果大家有睇winter on fire<br />\n<br />\n親俄羅斯政府倒台後，總統走佬去俄羅斯拎政治庇護<br />\n<br />\n震壓示威既別爾庫特部隊直頭走佬去俄羅斯，收編入俄羅斯國家近衛軍<br />\n<br />\n香港警察都需要被接收上北京做解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412e8e00a22a3e157d70b46bf82335962094c2e3","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4751cdfb053d54691f160471f525debf5e432f","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"08ea335b943dbfab268bf9466546999495c4a1f5","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9dfe156c74b0d6f13546d700ca3e9f6f43f38c69","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"727尋找元朗隱世美食"},{"pid":"d6b760eb824e4a4107f1c3ed213398f589af52e4","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6f93c887444f8fe6b3c9448304876454d2f4431b","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bf4364b75673ec3364febe5f7f7e94cdddb592e4","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"88b637ae568b700519e02a155d190a7e4fe59e3b","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f345aaa98c3d3deec09b8ac8a97e005c740759ca","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"0c8b0f37654c133fb1e458b4e5ff46821fede29f","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7eb25119cedba2700bca05657faf95bb1cc958af","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"10連無難度"},{"pid":"18bc577828ed4999b08ef715bc2efd50313f9b3b","tid":1368740,"uid":156891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"政府成日推大灣區，最岩送哂d差佬上去"},{"pid":"1b73b3a1dc29eaab528dc783f7ab1995ea2596eb","tid":1368740,"uid":1568